projects.title: Software Engineer
projects.description: I work with an Agile cross-disciplinary team providing real-time software solutions with C++, C#, Python, and Java. I built a Jenkins Pipeline stage in Groovy that used the Linux shell to validate 40 XML files in 2 Git repositories. I implemented a REST API call in C# that GPNTS automation tests use to retrieve data from another service.

projects.title: Software Engineer
projects.description: I participated in a highly collaborative Agile environment and developed real-time software solutions in C++ and Java. I implemented 3 messages in C++ that provided data to C++ services and the Java frontend.
